-   <span data-ttu-id="d78ba-117"><xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SemanticValue.Value%2A> プロパティが `null` です。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d78ba-117">The <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SemanticValue.Value%2A> property is `null`.</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="d78ba-118">1.0 の場合は、人為的なセマンティックの信頼レベル (によって返される<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SemanticValue.Confidence%2A>)。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d78ba-118">An artificial semantic confidence level of 1.0 (returned by <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SemanticValue.Confidence%2A>).</span></span>  
  
